To run (and debug) in Visual Studio Code use the "Debug todo-api" in Debug options:
![VScode debug](images/vscode_debug.png)


After the server starts, use http://localhost:3000/docs for swagger:
![Swagger](images/swagger.png)


Sample .env file for local debugging (using SQLite DB)
=======================================================
```.env
PORT=3000
DB_TYPE=sqlite
DB_SQLITE_PATH=./sqlite/database.sqlite
```
